{"tid":2130142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FedEx機師工會不滿香港檢疫安排 促暫停香港業務","createTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:24:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d27e8ac17675579b3c7d3fe3f98d1aa0b4a1995","tid":2130142,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"代表聯邦快遞(FedEx)機師的工會ALPA呼籲公司暫停在香港的業務，不滿員工遭受港府極嚴格的檢疫安排<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，3名感染新型冠狀病毒的FedEx機師在沒有症狀下，被迫入院長達10日。而多名檢測為陰性的機師由於被列為密切接觸者，亦需要入住環境惡劣的政府隔離營地。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦快遞發表聲明指，公司已經與政府當局充分合作，會為需要入院治療或隔離的機組人員提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1030980/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1030980%2F2&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6aVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=2e74625d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1030980/2</a>"},{"pid":"307478512d3a2d1cdf56360401652353bc86fe8c","tid":2130142,"uid":232583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882d90d9daab85576256aa26a85d09eba5adef4d","tid":2130142,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59f2b05fce0b7b910397bb8a4785c1f55abe1ed5","tid":2130142,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"Before arriving, crew must test negative for the virus within 48 hours of boarding. On arrival, they will be tested again and must self isolate without going into the community, the government said.<br />\n<br />\nThere have been numerous instances of aircrew flouting quarantine rules, including a FedEx pilot who flew from Boston to Hong Kong.